lead_paragraph: Robert Lewandowski struck twice and Arjen Robben netted with a rare diving header as champions Bayern Munich came from a goal down to win 3-1 at Mainz 05 to reclaim top spot in the Bundesliga on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Lewandowski, Robben Goals Put Bayern Back on Top
headline.main: Lewandowski, Robben Goals Put Bayern Back on Top
